<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">9月已至！</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">秋高气爽，阳光正好</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">给自己一个全新的目标</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">每天多一点努力</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">未来多一份选择</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">9月考试日历</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">收藏，加油</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886736845.png" alt="1756886736845.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886736845.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">要考证的小伙伴</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">来看9月专业技术人员职业资格考试时间表</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886802050.png" alt="1756886802050.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886802050.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886824300.png" alt="1756886824300.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1756886824300.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">祝大家都能取得理想的成绩！</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">来源：江西省教育厅</span></p>